    <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Effective date: September 17, 2025</p>

    <p>Accessio ("we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have. This is a simple, plain-language summary — not legal advice.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
