        <li><strong>Personal information:</strong> when you register or contact us we may collect your name, email address, and other information you provide.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> information about how you use the site (pages visited, timestamps, device/browser information, IP address) collected automatically.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies:</strong> to enable features, remember preferences, and analyze site usage.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
